{% extends "src/_includes/default.njk" %}

{% block title %}Julian Rachele | About{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="mx-10 my-4 px-4">
  <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl text-purple-900">About me</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
  <div>
  <p>I am a 22 year old graduate student from Greenville, South Carolina. I was born in Arizona though and lived there for 8 years, so is that where I'm actually "from"? Seems to be a bit ambiguous. I'm American, I guess. Like many scatterbrained children of the internet, I have a wide range of interests of varying utility.</p>
  <p>Food is basically everything. We are all spinning out of control on this spec of dust, so why not enjoy some tasty flavor combinations?</p>
  </div>
  <img src="img/self_portrait.png" class="w-48 md:w-auto h-auto md:h-32 lg:h-24 my-12 lg:my-4 ml-4 rounded-full">
  </div>
  <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl text-purple-900 py-2">Interests</h1>
  <ul class="list-disc mx-4">
    <li>Cooking</li>
    <li>Video games</li>
    <li>Programming</li>
    <li>Design</li>
    <li>Mind-numbing reality TV</li>
    <li>Foreign languages? I am a serial dabbler. Get really obsessed and motivated to learn a language then come back down to Earth and lose motivation after a couple months. Decent at French though</li>
  </ul>
  <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl text-purple-900 py-2">Projects</h1>
  <div class="shadow-md bg-gray-800 text-gray-200 m-8 p-6 rounded" x-data="{open: false}">
    <div class="flex items-center">
      <a href="https://redcraft.readthedocs.io" class="w-auto h-20 mr-4"><img src="img/redcraft_logo.png"></a>
      
      <div class="description">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center">
        <a href="https://redcraft.readthedocs.io"><h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mr-4">REDCRAFT</h1></a>
        </div>
        <p>REDCRAFT is a software suite that will computationally determine protein structure from Residual Dipolar Couplings.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Button for opening card -->
      <div class="ml-4">
        <div @click="open = !open;" class="flex items-center cursor-pointer px-3 py-2 text-gray-200 hover:text-gray-600" :class="{'transform rotate-180': open}">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Collapsed content -->
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col mt-8" :class="{'hidden': !open}">
      <hr class="mb-4 border-gray-700">
      <p>Over the course of two years, I have worked on REDCRAFT, a project created by Homayoun Valafar at the University of South Carolina in 2003.</p>
      <p>The project is a C++ project that outputs PDB files based on RDC files provided in the universal <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/nsmb.3041"><u>NEF</u></a> format.</p>
      <p>As far as what I have done specifically:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-2">
        <li>Created UI in Qt5 (C++) to leverage REDCRAFT's command line utilities</li>
        <li>Updated REDCRAFT to C++11 and to CMake, building REDCRAFT/REDCAT libraries and GUI simultaneously</li>
        <li>Updated documentation to be generated on commit, using <em>readthedocs.io</em></li>
        <li>Introduced unit tests and helped set up Continuous Deployment pipeline</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}